      "content": "wait, you said \"a huge, slow-moving horde of interest\" eating the principal? that's a weird way to put it lol. anyway, can you just be more specific with the numbers? if my payment is 2100, how much of that is actually principal in year 5 vs year 25? i'm trying to see if it's worth paying extra to get ahead of it.",
